{"data":[{"date":"16:46 15/06","title":"Louis Saha: \"Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/6/louis-saha-phap-co-the-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Louis Saha ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, c\u1ef1u sao MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Les Bleus ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u0103ng quang t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Louis Saha \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPaul Pogba v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n t\u1edbi Nga v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/top-5-ung-vien-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-brazil-duc-chua-la-gi-so-voi-ho-421-188520.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span>. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Les Blues c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Brazil l\u00e0 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Louis Saha ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Louis Saha ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/louis-saha-phap-co-the-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Saha \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Euro 2016, Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Didier Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLouis Saha ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, c\u1ef1u sao MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Les Bleus ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u0103ng quang t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\"Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t gi\u1ecfi \u1edf m\u1ecdi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed. V\u1eady t\u1ea1i sao h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch? T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Ph\u00e1p \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup sau 20 n\u0103m ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cDeschamps \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i phong \u0111\u1ed9. Ph\u00e1p h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Saha \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1p n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C v\u1edbi \u00dac, Peru v\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, Salah tin r\u1eb1ng Les Bleus s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u. C\u1ef1u sao MU c\u0169ng tin r\u1eb1ng h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dinh cao cua Saha la khi anh khoac ao M.U\" title=\"\u0110\u1ec9nh cao c\u1ee7a Saha l\u00e0 khi anh kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2013/8/Untitled-(54)-20138913494.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Saha tin h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n. H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t gi\u00fap h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng thua, nh\u01b0ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ghi b\u00e0n. Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cH\u1ecd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0 Kylian Mbappe, Antoine Griezmann, Ousmane Dembele\u2026 V\u1edbi h\u00e0ng <br>\r\nc\u00f4ng si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng, Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00e1p s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p \u00dac \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Peru v\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"199","checkdouble":"188562"},{"date":"17:05 15/06","title":"\"Ai C\u1eadp kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o Mohamed Salah\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/6/ai-cap-khong-nen-ky-vong-qua-nhieu-vao-mohamed-salah.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ahmed Hassan ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mohamed Salah, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ai C\u1eadp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111i qu\u00e1 s\u00e2u \u1edf World Cup 2018 n\u1ebfu ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Salah.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mohamed Salah b\u00e1o tin vui cho Ai C\u1eadp</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mohamed Salah d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng vai trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C1 2018, theo \u0111\u00f3 anh g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 Sergio Ramos c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ahmed Hassan ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mohamed Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ahmed Hassan ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mohamed Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/ai-cap-khong-nen-ky-vong-qua-nhieu-vao-mohamed-salah.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mohamed Salah \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Salah \u0111\u1ebfn khi World Cup 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 2 tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa l\u00e0 di\u1ec5n ra, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c. \u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ai-cap-nhan-tin-vui-bat-ngo-tu-thanh-salah-421-188498.html\" target=\"_blank\">Salah \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i</span>, ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Uruguay v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tin c\u1ef1c vui v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp v\u1edbi Salah l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, ch\u00ednh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Liverpool, Salah c\u0169ng duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao. Theo \u0111\u00f3, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 ghi t\u1edbi 44 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 32 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ai C\u1eadp kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o Salah</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ahmed Hassan ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mohamed Salah, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ai C\u1eadp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111i qu\u00e1 s\u00e2u \u1edf World Cup 2018 n\u1ebfu ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Salah.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Ai Cap xac nhan Salah binh phuc chan thuong\" title=\"HLV Ai C\u1eadp x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Salah b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/World-Cup-2018-Nhung-dieu-can-biet-truoc-tran-Ai-Cap-vs-Uruguay-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ahmed Hassan cho r\u1eb1ng Ai C\u1eadp kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o</span>\u00a0Salah\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cAi C\u1eadp \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. V\u1edbi b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh, Ai C\u1eadp c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ea3i d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i. Ai C\u1eadp kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o Salah \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 World Cup\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAhmed Hassan \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng 4 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u Phi c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y tin r\u1eb1ng Salah ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"198","checkdouble":"188563"},{"date":"16:50 15/06","title":"S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 10: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea3ng G","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-10-nhan-dinh-bang-g.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 scandal l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m qua, v\u1ee5 sa th\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Lopetegui s\u1ebd g\u00e2y ra \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t x\u1ea5u t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00ean li\u00ean quan. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u s\u1eafp x\u1ea3y ra trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nReal Madrid mang ti\u1ebfng x\u1ea5u<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Zidane, HLV \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 cho Real Madrid 3 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap C1 ch\u1ec9 sau 2 n\u0103m r\u01b0\u1ee1i c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu. H\u1ecd \u00e2m th\u1ea7m ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia Julen Lopetegui, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c h\u00fat c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u00e1ng b\u00e0n, n\u1ebfu Lopetegui chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb h\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, HLV 51 tu\u1ed5i m\u1edbi gia h\u1ea1n c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 3 tu\u1ea7n, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n b\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u00e0o ch\u1eefa b\u1edfi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ea3y ra sau v\u1ee5 sa th\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Lopetegui h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ea3y ra sau v\u1ee5 sa th\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Lopetegui h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Nhung-dieu-xay-ra-sau-vu-sa-thai-cua-Lopetegui-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lopetegui ra m\u1eaft CLB Ho\u00e0ng gia sau khi b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho ai c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng, khi h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a v\u1ee5 sa th\u1ea3i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 &ldquo;th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea1m&rdquo; ch\u00ednh, d\u00f9 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng vui v\u1ebb g\u00ec khi nh\u1eadn l\u1ea1i &ldquo;t\u1ed9i nh\u00e2n&rdquo; c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Luis Rubiales kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng b\u1ecf qua \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft ch\u1eebng s\u1ebd c\u00f2n x\u1eed \u00e9p Real \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c khi ng\u1ed3i chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Los Blancos l\u00e0 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c n\u00e0o. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 ch\u00ednh Zidane, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111em v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 c\u0169ng su\u00fdt b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i (n\u1ebfu \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng&hellip; t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc). Nh\u00ecn sang Julen Lopetegui, gi\u1edd \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi ng\u1ecdn n\u00fai th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, m\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u0169ng b\u1ecb k\u00e9o xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ef1c s\u00e2u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u0111em Real ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi, Lopetegui \u0111\u1eebng hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng &ldquo;Judas&rdquo; Lopetegui bay gh\u1ebf s\u1edbm l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vu sa thai cua Lopetegui se khien Real Madrid gap nhieu van de\" title=\"V\u1ee5 sa th\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Lopetegui s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Real Madrid g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/loperez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>V\u1ee5 sa th\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Lopetegui s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Real Madrid g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>De Gea \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 \u0111\u00e3 hi\u1ec3n hi\u1ec7n trong \u0111\u1ea7u C\u0110V Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, khi Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 De Gea. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lopetegui ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, khi \u00f4ng t\u1eebng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y d\u1eabn d\u1eaft De Gea trong c\u00e1c c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1ebb \u1edf \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sergio Ramos li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u1edf l\u1eddi ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o, trong khi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f2 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean &ldquo;d\u00ed mic&rdquo; v\u00e0 h\u1ecfi De Gea v\u1ec1 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Real. &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i M.U&rdquo; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam, &ldquo;nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c&rdquo;, \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng m\u1eebng th\u1ea7m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n xoay ng\u01b0\u1ee3c 180 \u0111\u1ed9, b\u1edfi m\u00e0n \u0111i \u0111\u00eam kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tha th\u1ee9 c\u1ee7a Julen Lopetegui.</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De gea va Lopetegui\" title=\"De gea va Lopetegui\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/goc-nhin-hlv-lopetegui-cua-real-muon-mua-de-gea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>De Gea kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng theo b\u01b0\u1edbc \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y Lopetegui</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div><br>\r\nCh\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean khi Lopetegui b\u1ecb &ldquo;\u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ed5&rdquo; kh\u1ecfi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Real Madrid cu\u1ed1ng cu\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Alisson Becker &ndash; th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o AS Roma. H\u1ecd bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi scandal m\u1edbi n\u00e0y, l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2u k\u00e9o De Gea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t, v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n sang m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u euro s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real v\u00e0 Roma \u0111\u1ed3ng thu\u1eadn, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a ng\u01b0\u1eddi vui m\u1eebng nh\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Man United. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda th\u01b0\u1eddng ni\u00ean n\u1eefa, khi n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Los Blancos c\u00f2n \u0111ang g\u1eb7p tr\u1ee5c tr\u1eb7c l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn t\u00ednh ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u1ee5 sa th\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Lopetegui th\u1ebf n\u00e0o ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa, \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn g\u00e2y ra \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng x\u1ea5u t\u1edbi \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, scandal n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ra t\u1ed5n h\u1ea1i cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c b\u00ean, t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh Lopetegui, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Luis Rubiales, Real Madrid \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga. Ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua, Sergio Ramos th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n su\u00fdt t\u1ea9n Ng\u00e0i Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ramos phat bieu truoc tran Tay Ban Nha vs Bo Dao Nha\" title=\"Ramos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/ramos-phat-bieu-soc-truoc-tran-tay-ban-nha-vs-bo-dao-nha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 tinh th\u1ea7n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 ch\u1eb3ng m\u1ea5y t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Real Madrid &ndash; v\u1edbi Ramos \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u, c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Barca, \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn T\u00e2y Ban Nha g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam scandal n\u00e0y, qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u0103m 2010 m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean, ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Lopetegui &ndash; Fernando Hierro c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Real.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i l\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7. V\u1edbi \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n r\u1ec7u r\u00e3 v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t tinh th\u1ea7n, tr\u1ea3i qua c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup, kh\u00f4ng l\u1ea1 n\u1ebfu T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y &ndash; ch\u1ee9 \u0111\u1eebng n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/lopetegui-bat-khoc-trong-ngay-ra-mat-real-madrid-180-188509.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/lopetegui-bat-khoc-trong-ngay-ra-mat-real-madrid.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/lopetegui-bat-khoc-trong-ngay-ra-mat-real-madrid-180-188509.html\">Lopetegui b\u1eadt kh\u00f3c trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga di\u1ec5n ra tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c World Cup 2018 gi\u1eefa Nga vs Saudi Arabia, th\u00ec t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Real Madrid t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o quan tr\u1ecdng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-1h-ngay-166-khi-bo-tot-lac-loi-421-188527.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/nhan-dinh-bdn-vs-tbn-va-nhung-du-doan-vang-bongda24h.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-1h-ngay-166-khi-bo-tot-lac-loi-421-188527.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha (1h ng\u00e0y 16/6): Khi &ldquo;B\u00f2 t\u00f3t&rdquo; l\u1ea1c l\u1ed1i&hellip;</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 2 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i HLV Lopetegui. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng h\u1ec7 l\u1ee5y gh\u00ea g\u1edbm v\u00e0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"197","checkdouble":"188564"},{"date":"16:54 15/06","title":"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n, HAGL g\u00f3p 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/u19-viet-nam-cong-bo-danh-sach-sang-trung-quoc-tap-huan-hagl-gop-5-cai-ten.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch 25 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n nh\u1eb1m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 v\u00e0 U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m. </h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian mi\u1ec7t m\u00e0i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n PVF, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i H\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch, HAGL g\u00f3p 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch, HAGL g\u00f3p 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/AZ4A9834.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n b\u1ed5 \u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng V-League v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t th\u00ec trong chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i n\u00e0y, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 mang theo 25 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ra nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 v\u00e0 U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m.\u00a0</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 \u00fd th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 trong su\u1ed1t giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u1eeba qua.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u01b0a t\u1eadp h\u1ee3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t do m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u01b0\u1edbng l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 h\u1ea1ng Nh\u00ec QG nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n t\u1eebng c\u00f9ng \u0110T U20 VN tham d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup 2017 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh quan \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u01b0 duy ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u\u00a0 th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00f4m nay, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 10 ng\u00e0y t\u1eeb 16/6 \u0111\u1ebfn 25/6 t\u1edbi. Tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t b\u1ea1n, \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u 3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ng\u00e0y 17/6, 20/6 v\u00e0 23/6 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande (B) v\u00e0 CLB Meizhou Meixian Techand FC \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Trung Qu\u1ed1c. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 1/7 t\u1edbi 14/7 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Danh sach U19 Viet Nam\" title=\"Danh s\u00e1ch U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/DS-U19-tap-huan-TQ.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Danh s\u00e1ch U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vck-u19-chau-a-2018-co-hoi-nao-cho-u19-viet-nam-168-186585.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/18/vck-u19-chau-a-2018-co-hoi-nao-cho-u19-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vck-u19-chau-a-2018-co-hoi-nao-cho-u19-viet-nam-168-186585.html\">VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nL\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 t\u1ea1i Jarkata, Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn ch\u00e2u \u00c1 l\u00e0 U19 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, U19 \u00dac. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-trieu-tap-31-cau-thu-u19-viet-nam-de-mo-ve-world-cup-168-186380.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/20/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-trieu-tap-31-cau-thu-u19-viet-nam-de-mo-ve-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-trieu-tap-31-cau-thu-u19-viet-nam-de-mo-ve-world-cup-168-186380.html\">HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp 31 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 m\u01a1 v\u00e9 World Cup</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eb1m t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n k\u1ef3 t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup 2 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp 31 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam cho \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"196","checkdouble":"188565"},{"date":"16:57 15/06","title":"World Cup 2018: Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/world-cup-2018-nhung-dieu-can-biet-truoc-tran-ai-cap-vs-uruguay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c c\u00e2n n\u00e3o gi\u1eefa Ai C\u1eadp v\u00e0 Uruguay. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ti\u1ebfp theo c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga, ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a World Cup s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Cu\u1ed9c so t\u00e0i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 gi\u1eefa Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay \u1edf s\u00e2n Ekaterinburg. Uruguay l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Hector Cuper x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Salah \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Uruguay. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng Ai C\u1eadp c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-ai-cap-va-nhung-du-doan-khong-tuong-421-188535.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay</span> s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ai C\u1eadp</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng FIFA:</strong> 45</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean: </strong>Hector Cuper</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng:</strong> Essam El-Hadary<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"World Cup 2018 Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"World Cup 2018 Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/World-Cup-2018-Nhung-dieu-can-biet-truoc-tran-Ai-Cap-vs-Uruguay-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Salah k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Cuper, Ai C\u1eadp l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 hay nh\u1ea5t. H\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ed1 th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u01a1 h\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 tung ra nh\u1eefng c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1edd \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p si\u00eau sao c\u1ee7a Salah.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ai C\u1eadp ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1 thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Hai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Elneny v\u00e0 Hamed ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 hai trung v\u1ec7 d\u00e2ng cao. C\u1ea3 hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. Ri\u00eang Hamed lu\u00f4n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khen t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mohamed Salah s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i trong khi Mahmoud &lsquo;Trezeguet&rsquo; tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. Abdallah El-Said ch\u01a1i trong vai tr\u00f2 s\u1ed1 10. V\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp. Mohsen nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1eefa \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp l\u00e0 Ramadan Sobhi. \u1ede \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 21, Sobhi \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang l\u00ean c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp. Nhi\u1ec1u tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ebfn Sobhi \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng El-Hadary \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t t\u1eebng tham d\u1ef1 World Cup. V\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 45 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u cho Ai C\u1eadp. Trung v\u1ec7 Hegazy c\u1ee7a West Brom th\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4i luy\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh \u1edf Premier League. V\u00ec v\u1eady, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean mong ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0 ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nga.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Uruguay</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng FIFA:</strong> 14</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean:</strong> Oscar Tabarez</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng: </strong>Diego Godin<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Uruguay gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 t\u1edbi World Cup \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c Nam M\u1ef9 ch\u1ec9 sau Brazil v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u chuy\u00ean gia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Uruguay t\u1eebng kh\u00e1 gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp. H\u1ecd x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 d\u1ef1a nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. Nh\u01b0ng vi\u1ec7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Uruguay \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Uruguay xep thu 2 vong loai\" title=\"Uruguay xep thu 2 vong loai\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/DT-Uruguay-tai-World-Cup-2018-Duong-ta-thang-tien-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Uruguay s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Uruguay l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7. C\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i Godin v\u00e0 Gimenez thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t \u0103n \u00fd trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Atletico v\u00e0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng khi\u1ebfn cho b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0o c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng hai v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00e1c \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9 an to\u00e0n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. Varela v\u00e0 Caceres l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Nh\u01b0ng Caceres th\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p trong khi Varela ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Uruguay th\u00ec mang \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 an t\u00e2m h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u1ebb \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i. Bentancur c\u1ee7a Juventus v\u00e0 Vecino l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Nandez v\u00e0 Rodriguez s\u1eafm vai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh. \u1ede \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 22, Nandez \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Boca Juniors. Anh v\u1eeba ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, l\u1ea1i v\u1eeba c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Suarez v\u00e0 Cavani l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 hai trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi hi\u1ec7n nay. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c n\u00e0o \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n: \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i th\u00fa v\u1ecb gi\u1eefa h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u0169 b\u00e3o c\u1ee7a Uruguay. Nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, Uruguay s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng si\u00eau sao \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. V\u00e0 khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi tay th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Tabarez.</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-ai-cap-va-nhung-du-doan-khong-tuong-421-188535.html\">Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u Uruguay vs Ai C\u1eadp</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-ai-cap-vs-uruguay-19h-ngay-156-salah-co-hay-khong-khong-quan-trong-421-188524.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay (19h ng\u00e0y 15/6): Salah c\u00f3 hay kh\u00f4ng, kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng&hellip;</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"195","checkdouble":"188566"},{"date":"17:01 15/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ea3y ra sau m\u00e0n \u201cc\u01b0\u1edbp d\u00e2u\u201d c\u1ee7a Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/nhung-dieu-xay-ra-sau-man-cuop-dau-cua-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 scandal l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m qua, v\u1ee5 sa th\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Lopetegui s\u1ebd g\u00e2y ra \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t x\u1ea5u t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00ean li\u00ean quan. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u s\u1eafp x\u1ea3y ra trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nReal Madrid mang ti\u1ebfng x\u1ea5u<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Zidane, HLV \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 cho Real Madrid 3 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap C1 ch\u1ec9 sau 2 n\u0103m r\u01b0\u1ee1i c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu. H\u1ecd \u00e2m th\u1ea7m ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia Julen Lopetegui, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c h\u00fat c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u00e1ng b\u00e0n, n\u1ebfu Lopetegui chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb h\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, HLV 51 tu\u1ed5i m\u1edbi gia h\u1ea1n c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 3 tu\u1ea7n, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n b\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u00e0o ch\u1eefa b\u1edfi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ea3y ra sau v\u1ee5 sa th\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Lopetegui h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ea3y ra sau v\u1ee5 sa th\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Lopetegui h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Nhung-dieu-xay-ra-sau-vu-sa-thai-cua-Lopetegui-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lopetegui ra m\u1eaft CLB Ho\u00e0ng gia sau khi b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho ai c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng, khi h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a v\u1ee5 sa th\u1ea3i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 &ldquo;th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea1m&rdquo; ch\u00ednh, d\u00f9 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng vui v\u1ebb g\u00ec khi nh\u1eadn l\u1ea1i &ldquo;t\u1ed9i nh\u00e2n&rdquo; c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Luis Rubiales kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng b\u1ecf qua \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft ch\u1eebng s\u1ebd c\u00f2n x\u1eed \u00e9p Real \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c khi ng\u1ed3i chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Los Blancos l\u00e0 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c n\u00e0o. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 ch\u00ednh Zidane, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111em v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 c\u0169ng su\u00fdt b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i (n\u1ebfu \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng&hellip; t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc). Nh\u00ecn sang Julen Lopetegui, gi\u1edd \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi ng\u1ecdn n\u00fai th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, m\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u0169ng b\u1ecb k\u00e9o xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ef1c s\u00e2u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u0111em Real ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi, Lopetegui \u0111\u1eebng hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng &ldquo;Judas&rdquo; Lopetegui bay gh\u1ebf s\u1edbm l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vu sa thai cua Lopetegui se khien Real Madrid gap nhieu van de\" title=\"V\u1ee5 sa th\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Lopetegui s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Real Madrid g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/loperez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>V\u1ee5 sa th\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Lopetegui s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Real Madrid g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>De Gea \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 \u0111\u00e3 hi\u1ec3n hi\u1ec7n trong \u0111\u1ea7u C\u0110V Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, khi Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 De Gea. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lopetegui ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, khi \u00f4ng t\u1eebng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y d\u1eabn d\u1eaft De Gea trong c\u00e1c c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1ebb \u1edf \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sergio Ramos li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u1edf l\u1eddi ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o, trong khi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f2 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean &ldquo;d\u00ed mic&rdquo; v\u00e0 h\u1ecfi De Gea v\u1ec1 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Real. &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i M.U&rdquo; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam, &ldquo;nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c&rdquo;, \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng m\u1eebng th\u1ea7m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n xoay ng\u01b0\u1ee3c 180 \u0111\u1ed9, b\u1edfi m\u00e0n \u0111i \u0111\u00eam kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tha th\u1ee9 c\u1ee7a Julen Lopetegui.</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De gea va Lopetegui\" title=\"De gea va Lopetegui\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/goc-nhin-hlv-lopetegui-cua-real-muon-mua-de-gea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>De Gea kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng theo b\u01b0\u1edbc \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y Lopetegui</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div><br>\r\nCh\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean khi Lopetegui b\u1ecb &ldquo;\u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ed5&rdquo; kh\u1ecfi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Real Madrid cu\u1ed1ng cu\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Alisson Becker &ndash; th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o AS Roma. H\u1ecd bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi scandal m\u1edbi n\u00e0y, l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2u k\u00e9o De Gea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t, v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n sang m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u euro s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real v\u00e0 Roma \u0111\u1ed3ng thu\u1eadn, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a ng\u01b0\u1eddi vui m\u1eebng nh\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Man United. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda th\u01b0\u1eddng ni\u00ean n\u1eefa, khi n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Los Blancos c\u00f2n \u0111ang g\u1eb7p tr\u1ee5c tr\u1eb7c l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn t\u00ednh ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u1ee5 sa th\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Lopetegui th\u1ebf n\u00e0o ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa, \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn g\u00e2y ra \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng x\u1ea5u t\u1edbi \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, scandal n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ra t\u1ed5n h\u1ea1i cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c b\u00ean, t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh Lopetegui, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Luis Rubiales, Real Madrid \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga. Ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua, Sergio Ramos th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n su\u00fdt t\u1ea9n Ng\u00e0i Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ramos phat bieu truoc tran Tay Ban Nha vs Bo Dao Nha\" title=\"Ramos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/ramos-phat-bieu-soc-truoc-tran-tay-ban-nha-vs-bo-dao-nha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 tinh th\u1ea7n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 ch\u1eb3ng m\u1ea5y t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Real Madrid &ndash; v\u1edbi Ramos \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u, c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Barca, \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn T\u00e2y Ban Nha g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam scandal n\u00e0y, qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u0103m 2010 m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean, ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Lopetegui &ndash; Fernando Hierro c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Real.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i l\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7. V\u1edbi \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n r\u1ec7u r\u00e3 v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t tinh th\u1ea7n, tr\u1ea3i qua c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup, kh\u00f4ng l\u1ea1 n\u1ebfu T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y &ndash; ch\u1ee9 \u0111\u1eebng n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/lopetegui-bat-khoc-trong-ngay-ra-mat-real-madrid-180-188509.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/lopetegui-bat-khoc-trong-ngay-ra-mat-real-madrid.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/lopetegui-bat-khoc-trong-ngay-ra-mat-real-madrid-180-188509.html\">Lopetegui b\u1eadt kh\u00f3c trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga di\u1ec5n ra tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c World Cup 2018 gi\u1eefa Nga vs Saudi Arabia, th\u00ec t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Real Madrid t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o quan tr\u1ecdng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-1h-ngay-166-khi-bo-tot-lac-loi-421-188527.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/nhan-dinh-bdn-vs-tbn-va-nhung-du-doan-vang-bongda24h.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-1h-ngay-166-khi-bo-tot-lac-loi-421-188527.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha (1h ng\u00e0y 16/6): Khi &ldquo;B\u00f2 t\u00f3t&rdquo; l\u1ea1c l\u1ed1i&hellip;</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 2 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i HLV Lopetegui. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng h\u1ec7 l\u1ee5y gh\u00ea g\u1edbm v\u00e0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"194","checkdouble":"188567"},{"date":"17:30 15/06","title":"Rio Ferdinand ch\u1ec9 ra c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/3/rio-ferdinand-chi-ra-cai-ten-choi-xuat-sac-nhat-o-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Rio Ferdinand ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Paul Pogba, c\u1ef1u sao MU tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 \u1edf World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pogba l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110T Ph\u00e1p d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, Les Bleus \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch sau 20 n\u0103m ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i. Paul Pogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Nga.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rio Ferdinand ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Paul Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Rio Ferdinand ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Paul Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/3/rio-ferdinand-chi-ra-cai-ten-choi-xuat-sac-nhat-o-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 25, Pogba \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i sung s\u1ee9c nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 bao b\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a Kante v\u00e0 Matuidi, Pogba s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng minh cho Mourinho th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 anh s\u1ebd nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Pogba quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Rio Ferdinand tin Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Rio Ferdinand ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Paul Pogba, c\u1ef1u sao MU tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 \u1edf World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba dang quyet tam the hien minh\" title=\"Pogba \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/pogba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rio Ferdinand tin r\u1eb1ng Pogba s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cPogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u00c1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e8 n\u1eb7ng l\u00ean vai Pogba, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua s\u1ee9c \u00e9p \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, m\u1ed9t khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u0103ng hoa Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u00f4i \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0o Pogba, t\u00f4i tin c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/sagna-tin-tuong-pogba-se-toa-sang-o-world-cup-2018-469-188536.html\" target=\"_blank\">Sagna c\u0169ng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Pogba</span>, c\u1ef1u sao Man City c\u0169ng tin r\u1eb1ng ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPogba s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p \u00dac, v\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"193","checkdouble":"188568"},{"date":"17:41 15/06","title":"\"T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n sau khi sa th\u1ea3i Lopetegui\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/tay-ban-nha-se-manh-hon-sau-khi-sa-thai-lopetegui.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Roberto Martinez tin r\u1eb1ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n sau khi sa th\u1ea3i Julen Lopetegui.</h2><h2>Martinez b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i Lopetegui</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nong-dt-tay-ban-nha-sa-thai-hlv-lopetegui-truoc-thoi-han-421-188412.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i</span> v\u00e0 thay th\u1ebf b\u1edfi Fernando Hierro ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi World Cup di\u1ec5n ra. Nguy\u00ean do l\u00e0 b\u1edfi Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1ec1 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac World Cup.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Roberto Martinez c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00f4ng tin Lopetegui b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i. Nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng tin r\u1eb1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ecb gi\u1ea3m \u0111i v\u00ec l\u00fd do n\u00e0y. B\u1edfi t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 La Roja s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee9ng s\u00e1t l\u1ea1i g\u1ea7n nhau \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2y Ban Nha sa th\u1ea3i Lopetegui S\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t B\u00f2 t\u00f3t m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2y Ban Nha sa th\u1ea3i Lopetegui S\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t B\u00f2 t\u00f3t m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/tay-ban-nha-se-manh-hon-sau-khi-sa-thai-lopetegui.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00e2y Ban Nha sa th\u1ea3i Lopetegui tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cTrong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1edfi \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i l\u1ea1i th\u1ea5y vi\u1ec7c T\u00e2y Ban Nha sa th\u1ea3i Lopetegui l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cLopetegui \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadt l\u1ef1c trong hai n\u0103m qua. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ebd t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng mong \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0 s\u1ebd th\u1eadt th\u00fa v\u1ecb khi th\u1ea5y t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng th\u1ebf n\u00e0o tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cM\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 di\u1ec5n ra theo hai h\u01b0\u1edbng. N\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ed1t ho\u1eb7c x\u1ea5u. Nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3. Ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh c\u00f9ng nhau v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ngh\u1ecbch c\u1ea3nh v\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Martinez lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Roberto Martinez c\u0169ng lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Thomas Vermaelen v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Vincent Kompany tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 g\u1eb7p Panama.<br>\r\n<em><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cVermaelen v\u00e0 Kompany \u0111ang t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n theo ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh ri\u00eang d\u00e0nh cho h\u1ecd. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd \u1edf l\u1ea1i kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n thay v\u00ec ra s\u00e2n t\u1eadp.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cH\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh 24 gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Panama. Cho t\u1edbi l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o cho h\u1ecd nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 HLV Lopetegui:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tbn-mat-dau-truoc-world-cup-2018-tia-sang-hy-vong-nao-le-loi-giua-chon-hon-mang-loan-lac-421-188570.html\">TBN \u201cm\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea7u\u201d tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup 2018: Tia s\u00e1ng hy v\u1ecdng n\u00e0o le l\u00f3i gi\u1eefa ch\u1ed1n h\u1ed7n mang, lo\u1ea1n l\u1ea1c?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-1h-ngay-166-khi-bo-tot-lac-loi-421-188527.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha (1h ng\u00e0y 16/6): Khi \u201cB\u00f2 t\u00f3t\u201d l\u1ea1c l\u1ed1i\u2026</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"192","checkdouble":"188569"},{"date":"17:25 15/06","title":"TBN \u201cm\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea7u\u201d tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup 2018: Tia s\u00e1ng hy v\u1ecdng n\u00e0o le l\u00f3i gi\u1eefa ch\u1ed1n h\u1ed7n mang, lo\u1ea1n l\u1ea1c?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/tbn-mat-dau-truoc-world-cup-2018-tia-sang-hy-vong-nao-le-loi-giua-chon-hon-mang-loan-lac.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>TBN sa th\u1ea3i HLV Lopetegui ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c World Cup 2018 \u2013 Khi th\u1ec3 di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean tr\u00ean v\u1eadn m\u1ec7nh th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ed1c gia nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng n\u00f3.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch Euro 2000 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda, Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c cam k\u1ebft m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea3i c\u00e1ch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc. Nhi\u1ec1u b\u1eb1ng HLV chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p, v\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 r\u00f3t r\u00e0o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n t\u0103ng m\u1ea1nh, trong khi c\u00e1c s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u0169ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 linh ho\u1ea1t h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 \u0111a n\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n sinh, c\u00f9ng nhau chinh chi\u1ebfn mang vinh quang v\u1ec1 cho T\u1ed5 qu\u1ed1c. Huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00e0u, t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed3ng sang b\u1ea1c v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf Brazil 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"TBN sa th\u1ea3i HLV Lopetegui Tia s\u00e1ng n\u00e0o le l\u00f3i gi\u1eefa ch\u1ed1n h\u1ed7n mang h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"TBN sa th\u1ea3i HLV Lopetegui Tia s\u00e1ng n\u00e0o le l\u00f3i gi\u1eefa ch\u1ed1n h\u1ed7n mang h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/Nhan-dinh-Bo-Dao-Nha-vs-Tay-Ban-Nha-1h-ngay-166-Bo-tot-lac-loi-hinh-anh.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>TBN sa th\u1ea3i HLV Lopetegui ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u0103m 2018, T\u00e2y Ban Nha quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng chu\u1ea9n m\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ea1o n\u00ean. Sa th\u1ea3i HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 48 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n World Cup g\u1eb7p \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00f4ng n\u1ed5i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1ea5y ti\u1ec1n l\u1ec7. \u0110\u1ed9t nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t cho c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y m\u1ea5t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01b0\u1edbng, v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbnh, kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e2u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nong-dt-tay-ban-nha-sa-thai-hlv-lopetegui-truoc-thoi-han-421-188412.html\" target=\"_blank\">TBN sa th\u1ea3i HLV Lopetegui</span>, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u01b0ng \u00edt th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n. Gi\u1edd th\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u00e2m l\u00fd, tinh th\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng th\u00f4i cho G\u0110KT Fernando Hierro c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng c\u00f2n ch\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ee7, hu\u1ed1ng h\u1ed3 b\u1ea5t t\u1eadn v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 k\u00e9o theo sau \u0111\u00f3. Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Real Madrid tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh v\u1eadt t\u1ebf th\u1ea7n cho m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 quan b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u01b0u ti\u00ean th\u1ec3 di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u1ebfu Brazil, m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1c cho c\u00fap v\u00e0ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, hy v\u1ecdng World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd xua tan \u00e1m \u1ea3nh b\u00f3ng ma qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c gieo r\u1eafc v\u00e0 v\u1eabn v\u1ea9n v\u01b0\u01a1ng su\u1ed1t 4 n\u0103m qua, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng c\u00f3 s\u1ee9 m\u1ec7nh c\u1ee9u r\u1ed7i linh h\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh, c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ea3 World Cup v\u00e0 Euro s\u1edbm ra v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng trong t\u1ee7i nh\u1ee5c, v\u1edbi 7 b\u00e0n thua t\u1eb7ng k\u00e8m t\u1eeb H\u00e0 Lan v\u00e0 Chile.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"TBN m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup 2018 Tia s\u00e1ng hy v\u1ecdng n\u00e0o le l\u00f3i gi\u1eefa ch\u1ed1n h\u1ed7n mang, lo\u1ea1n l\u1ea1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"TBN m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup 2018 Tia s\u00e1ng hy v\u1ecdng n\u00e0o le l\u00f3i gi\u1eefa ch\u1ed1n h\u1ed7n mang, lo\u1ea1n l\u1ea1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/TBN-mat-dau-truoc-World-Cup-2018-Tia-sang-hy-vong-nao-le-loi-giua-chon-hon-mang,-loan-lac-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1eb7t th\u1ec3 di\u1ec7n l\u00ean tr\u00ean v\u1eadn m\u1ec7nh c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Luis Rubiales th\u1eb3ng tay l\u00e0m chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cho \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ee9 T\u01b0 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u1ee7a Julen Lopetegui c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ec7m c\u1eadn m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t hai n\u0103m ng\u1ed3i gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 52 tu\u1ed5i. \u00d4ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh linh ho\u1ea1t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt h\u01a1n Vicente del Bosque, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1edfi m\u1edf c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap La Roja d\u00e0y d\u1eb7n ch\u1ecdn l\u1ef1a h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Lopetegui c\u00fai \u0111\u1ea7u ra \u0111i v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch HLV ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c duy nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha. 20 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 70%, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 th\u1ea3nh th\u01a1i b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p chung \u0111\u1ee5ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tbn-sa-thai-hlv-lopetegui-ngay-truoc-them-world-cup-2018-vi-cuoc-doi-nao-may-ai-biet-truoc-421-188462.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/Nhan-dinh-Bo-Dao-Nha-vs-Tay-Ban-Nha-1h-ngay-166-Bo-tot-lac-loi-hinh-anh.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tbn-sa-thai-hlv-lopetegui-ngay-truoc-them-world-cup-2018-vi-cuoc-doi-nao-may-ai-biet-truoc-421-188462.html\">TBN \u0111u\u1ed5i vi\u1ec7c HLV ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018: V\u00ec cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi n\u00e0o m\u1ea5y ai bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc!</span><br>\r\nV\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 24 ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 ng\u1eafn ng\u1ee7i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 h\u01a1n, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Julen Lopetegui r\u01a1i th\u1eb3ng m\u1ea1ch t\u1eeb thi\u00ean \u0111\u00e0ng xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c....</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u1eadm ch\u00e2n v\u00e0i gi\u1edd th\u00f4i trong ng\u00e0y 21/07/2016 \u0111\u00f3 th\u00f4i, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0110TQG l\u1edbn m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t HLV \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 tay m\u1ed9t CLB h\u1ea1ng hai \u1edf Anh, ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u00e0 Lopetegui g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn xong xu\u00f4i h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi\u2026 Wolverhampton Wanderers. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, T\u00e2y Ban Nha th\u1eddi b\u1ea5y gi\u1edd c\u0169ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 coi \u00f4ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ch\u1eefa ch\u00e1y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i, nh\u1eefng th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn d\u1ea7n d\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y s\u1eafc n\u00e9t \u1edf La Roja d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Lopetegui, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng v\u1ef1c d\u1eady tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eddi qu\u1ef5 ng\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c danh hi\u1ec7u World Cup th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia h\u1ebft \u1edf th\u00ec qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lopetegui ra mat CLB Hoang gia sau khi bi sa thai\" title=\"Lopetegui ra m\u1eaft CLB Ho\u00e0ng gia sau khi b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Nhung-dieu-xay-ra-sau-vu-sa-thai-cua-Lopetegui-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Julen Lopetegui th\u1eabn th\u1edd ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Lopetegui kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00f4 t\u1ed9i g\u00ec cho cam. S\u1ee9c h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn s\u1eb7c m\u00f9i c\u00e1m d\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb CLB v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 danh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1i t\u1eeb, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ngay c\u1ea3 li\u1ec1u l\u0129nh \u0111i \u0111\u00eam c\u0169ng \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e2m ch\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu Real Madrid ch\u1ec9 m\u1edf l\u1eddi th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o cho L\u0110B\u0110 T\u00e2y Ban Nha (RFEF) v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 5 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 v\u1ecb t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u01a1n gi\u1eadn m\u1ea5t kh\u00f4n c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Luis Rubiales ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch b\u1ecb qua m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 bi\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh th\u1eb1ng ng\u1ed1c, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 l\u1ebd r\u1ea5t th\u00edch nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t t\u1ee9c th\u00ec, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi c\u00f3 \u00fd th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4n l\u01b0\u1eddng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft m\u00ecnh. Ng\u00e0y mai khai m\u1ea1c World Cup r\u1ed3i? Qu\u00ean \u0111i! Th\u1ec3 di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean tr\u00ean v\u1eadn m\u1ec7nh th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ed1c gia dung d\u01b0\u1ee1ng n\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1, b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o v\u00e0 suy ngh\u0129 duy l\u00fd li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 lo s\u1ee3 r\u1eb1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m \u1edf Bernabeu s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Lopetegui sao nh\u00e3ng, m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung cho chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha? V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i c\u1ee9 cho \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed1i \u00e2u lo c\u1ee7a RFEF \u0111i, ch\u1eb3ng l\u1ebd h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng k\u1ebf s\u00e1ch sa th\u1ea3i HLV c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed g\u00e2y n\u00ean c\u01a1n bi\u1ebfn lo\u1ea1n, h\u1ed7n mang l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t thay v\u00ec c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3 \u00e2m \u1ec9 trong t\u1ea7m ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"doi hinh TBN tap luyen\" title=\"doi hinh TBN tap luyen\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/doi-hinh-TBN-tap-luyen.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>N\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft l\u1ea1i h\u01a1n hay tan t\u00e0nh m\u00e2y kh\u00f3i sau v\u1ee5 scandal n\u00e0y?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra trong l\u00f2ng n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda n\u00e0o, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u mong m\u1ecfi ki\u1ebfm t\u00ecm s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c quan tr\u1ea5n an tinh th\u1ea7n b\u1ea5n lo\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u0103m 2006 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t \u0110\u1ee9c, k\u1ef3 World Cup g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng ra ngo\u00e0i th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd sau b\u00ea b\u1ed1i v\u1ee5 scandal Calciopoli d\u00e0n x\u1ebfp t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ng\u00e0y 4/7, c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1 vi\u00ean Stefano Palazzi lu\u1eadn t\u1ed9i Juventus, AC Milan, Lazio v\u00e0 Fiorentina c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh ph\u1ea1t t\u1ed1ng c\u1ed5 kh\u1ecfi Serie A v\u00e0 gi\u00e1ng xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi. 5 ng\u00e0y sau, m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 bao g\u1ed3m 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eddi thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf nh\u1eefng CLB \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng cao c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ee9 4 \u1edf Berlin.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-1h-ngay-166-khi-bo-tot-lac-loi-421-188527.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/nhan-dinh-bdn-vs-tbn-va-nhung-du-doan-vang-bongda24h.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-1h-ngay-166-khi-bo-tot-lac-loi-421-188527.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha (1h ng\u00e0y 16/6): Khi \u201cB\u00f2 t\u00f3t\u201d l\u1ea1c l\u1ed1i\u2026</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 2 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i HLV Lopetegui. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng h\u1ec7 l\u1ee5y gh\u00ea g\u1edbm v\u00e0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u01a1 m\u00e0 li\u1ec7u r\u1eb1ng trong th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y, T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 h\u1ecdc ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd ch\u00fat g\u00ec v\u1ec1 tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u00edt ra c\u0169ng n\u00ean gi\u1ea3 t\u1ea1o v\u1ebb ngo\u00e0i m\u1eb7t v\u00ec quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i chung cho c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc, d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c? <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f3 l\u1eafm, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00f2ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Lopetegui, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea7u xin ho\u00e3n \u00e1n t\u1eed cho \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y v\u1eeba th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eeba t\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ea5y, m\u1ecdi n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u00edch trong c\u01a1n gi\u1eadn m\u00f9 qu\u00e1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5u xi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a Rubiales.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u1ebfu anh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tin r\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t b\u1eb1ng m\u1eb7t d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nhau ch\u1ec9 trong v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng th\u00f4i, anh c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-zidane-ra-di-su-ngot-ngat-cua-real-madrid-va-barcelona-180-188127.html\" target=\"_blank\">s\u1ef1 kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 ng\u1ed9t ng\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ee9 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f2</span> r\u1ed3i.</p>\r\n<h2><strong>Theo d\u00f2ng s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n TBN sa th\u1ea3i HLV Lopetegui ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c World Cup 2018:</strong><strong><br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-real-bo-nhiem-hlv-moi-thay-zidane-180-188332.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Real b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV m\u1edbi thay Zidane</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nong-dt-tay-ban-nha-sa-thai-hlv-lopetegui-truoc-thoi-han-421-188412.html\">N\u00d3NG: \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C sa th\u1ea3i HLV Lopetegui tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguyen-nhan-thuc-su-dang-sau-viec-hlv-lopetegui-bi-tbn-sa-thai-421-188413.html\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eb1ng sau vi\u1ec7c HLV Lopetegui b\u1ecb TBN sa th\u1ea3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chinh-thuc-tay-ban-nha-bo-nhiem-huyen-thoai-fernando-hierro-lam-hlv-thay-the-julen-lopentegui-421-188420.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Real Madrid thay th\u1ebf HLV Lopetegui</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cay-dang-roi-trai-tbn-lopetegui-nhan-cac-hoc-tro-bien-noi-dau-thanh-dong-luc-421-188446.html\">Cay \u0111\u1eafng r\u1eddi tr\u1ea1i TBN, Lopetegui nh\u1eafn c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 bi\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i \u0111au th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tbn-dai-loan-ramos-tan-nhau-voi-chu-tich-ngay-tren-san-tap-421-188503.html\">TBN \u0111\u1ea1i lo\u1ea1n: Ramos \u201ct\u1ea9n\u201d nhau v\u1edbi Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tay-ban-nha-co-nguy-co-bao-dong-sau-khi-lopetegui-ra-di-421-188457.html\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng sau khi Lopetegui ra \u0111i?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/judas-lopetegui-muoi-mat-tro-lai-tay-ban-nha-chuan-bi-ra-mat-real-madrid-180-188486.html\">Judas Lopetegui mu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/lopetegui-bat-khoc-trong-ngay-ra-mat-real-madrid-180-188509.html\">Lopetegui b\u1eadt kh\u00f3c trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"191","checkdouble":"188570"},{"date":"17:30 15/06","title":"Sao HAGL s\u1eafp ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng v\u00ec l\u1ed7i \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/15/sao-hagl-sap-phai-nhan-an-phat-nang-vi-loi-danh-nguoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a HAGL c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t ngu\u1ed9i t\u1eeb ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF sau h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 13 V-League 2018.</h2><h2>Sao HAGL s\u1eafp ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng v\u00ec l\u1ed7i \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh HAGL s\u1eafp ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh HAGL s\u1eafp ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/a_hoang_zing.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Trung v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa HAGL vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 13 V-League 2018, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a HAGL c\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u khi c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Douglas b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Douglas sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng kh\u00e1 gay g\u1eaft tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 l\u1ebd tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n Qu\u1ed1c H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng theo d\u00f5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng r\u00fat th\u1ebb cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng t\u1eeb d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, VFF \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c. Theo tin t\u1eeb ban \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh V-League 2018 cho bi\u1ebft chi\u1ec1u nay 15/6 s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn b\u0103ng h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 xem x\u00e9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng va ch\u1ea1m c\u1ee7a V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 Rosa Taudin Douglas. N\u1ebfu x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi phi th\u1ec3 thao, Ban \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh s\u1ebd l\u00e0m h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c g\u1eedi sang Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh cho r\u1eb1ng l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang xem x\u00e9t l\u1ea1i pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i t\u1eeb ph\u00eda BTC, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 d\u00e0nh cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u1ecb n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb: \u201cN\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sai, Ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ebd x\u1eed l\u00fd. CLB kh\u00f4ng bao che\u201d.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i V-League nh\u01b0 Omar hay Oseni \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t ngu\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng khi \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e0 n\u0103ng V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 b\u1edfi h\u00e0nh vi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"190","checkdouble":"188571"},{"date":"11:06 15/06","title":"Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nga sau tr\u1eadn h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Saudi Arabia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/mourinho-khen-ngoi-mot-cau-thu-nga-sau-tran-huy-diet-saudi-arabia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man United s\u1ebd c\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean mua l\u1ea1i Martial trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u1ecfi Old Trafford h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>MU t\u00ednh b\u00e1n Martial</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n MU s\u1ebd c\u00e0i c\u1eafm khi b\u00e1n Martial h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n MU s\u1ebd c\u00e0i c\u1eafm khi b\u00e1n Martial h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/13/tiet-lo-dieu-khoan-mu-se-cai-cam-khi-ban-martial.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU s\u1ebd b\u00e1n Martial h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Lamboley x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Martial \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay \u201cNh\u00e0 h\u00e1t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1\u201d h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u00d4ng cho r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Alexis Sanchez \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00f4ng l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn Martial m\u1ea5t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 sa s\u00fat.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t 18 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Premier League m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua. V\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 Martial \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tham d\u1ef1 World Cup c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Martial v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a HLV Mourinho \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Man United c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 Martial ra \u0111i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Mourinho s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Martial mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. V\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1eafng nghe nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i.</div>\r\n<h2>Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00e0i c\u1eafm th\u00eam c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Metro \u0111\u01b0a tin r\u1eb1ng Man United s\u1ebd c\u00e0i th\u00eam \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ea7n tr\u0103m ti\u1ec1n ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1ebfu c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c b\u00e1n Martial sau \u0111\u00f3. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Martial mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Man United lo ng\u1ea1i r\u1eb1ng Martial c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c. V\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf d\u0129 nhi\u00ean s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb 22 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ng\u1eb7t ngh\u00e8o.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Ed Woodward l\u00ean n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n n\u0103m 2013, Man United th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00ednh k\u00e8m nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n v\u00e0o trong c\u00e1c h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n h\u01b0\u1edfng 25% ti\u1ec1n ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau n\u00e0y v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u00e1n Michael Keane cho Burnley n\u0103m 2015. Man United c\u0169ng c\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua l\u1ea1i khi b\u00e1n Depay cho Lyon v\u00e0o n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU kh\u00e1c:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-se-de-martial-roi-mu-voi-mot-dieu-kien-172-188464.html\">Mourinho s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 Martial r\u1eddi MU v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-vu-sao-khung-psg-172-188458.html\">MU nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c m\u1eebng v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng PSG</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"189","checkdouble":"188537"},{"date":"10:30 15/06","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Anh \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tunisia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/day-doi-hinh-cua-anh-doi-dau-voi-tunisia.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Anh vs Tunisia d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Gareth Southgate quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, theo \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng G.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Anh ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Anh n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng G v\u1edbi B\u1ec9, Tunisia v\u00e0 Panama. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Tam s\u01b0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Tunisia.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e2y! \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Anh vs Tunisia - B\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u00e2y! \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Anh vs Tunisia - B\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Day!-Doi-hinh-Anh-vs-Tunisia---Bang-G-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T Anh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Tunisia\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Anh vs Tunisia d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Gareth Southgate quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, theo \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng G.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, theo m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin m\u1eadt t\u1eeb t\u1edd Metro, trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh, HLV Southgate \u0111\u00e3 chia th\u00e0nh 2 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh bao g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Southgate l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn bao g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 Kyle Walker v\u00e0 John Stones \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, Dele Alli v\u00e0 Jesse Lingard \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u00e0 Harry Kane v\u00e0 Raheem Sterling tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia, trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y HLV Southgate \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ra s\u00e2n ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c HLV Southgate ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec3n Anh th\u00e0nh 2 nh\u00f3m, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi Tunisia. Tam s\u01b0 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o t\u00e2m l\u00fd thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e2y! \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Anh \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tunisia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"\u0110\u00e2y! \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Anh \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tunisia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/day-doi-hinh-cua-anh-doi-dau-voi-tunisia.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Anh vs Tunisia\u00a0cho t\u1edd Metro d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Metro \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Anh g\u1eb7p Tunisia. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, HLV Southgate s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-5-2 v\u1edbi Jordan Pickford trong khung g\u1ed7. B\u1ed9 ba h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bao g\u1ed3m Harry Maguire, Kyle Walker v\u00e0 John Stones.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, Henderson, Alli v\u00e0 Lingard \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng. Henderson s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Lingard v\u00e0 Alli s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i cao h\u01a1n nh\u1eb1m h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede hai c\u00e1nh, Young v\u00e0 Kieran Trippier \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng, c\u1ea3 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i linh ho\u1ea1t trong vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7. Tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Raheem Sterling v\u00e0 Harry Kane.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"188","checkdouble":"188538"},{"date":"10:28 15/06","title":"BLV Quang Huy d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/blv-quang-huy-du-doan-the-nao-ve-tran-bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng B gi\u1eefa B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha, BLV Quang Huy \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa hai qu\u1ed1c gia tr\u00ean b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea3o Iberia n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BLV Quang Huy an tuong ve man ra mat cua DT Viet Nam\" title=\"BLV Quang Huy \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/3/26/blv-quang-huy-dt-viet-nam-da-the-khong-hanh-phuc-moi-la-la.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>BLV Quang Huy d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a \u1edf&nbsp;tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 1h00 r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai 16/6, c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u1ea3y l\u1eeda gi\u1eefa hai th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7n nay l\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Cu\u1ed9c th\u01b0 h\u00f9ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B khi m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 2 \u01afCV n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd cho t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i n\u00e0y, BLV Quang Huy \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c so t\u00e0i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. B\u00e1o D\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t d\u1eabn l\u1eddi v\u1ecb BLV b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e2u n\u0103m n\u00e0y cho hay: &ldquo;\u1ede b\u1ea3ng B, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha s\u1ebd l\u00e0 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i, T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i tiqui-taca \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m nay g\u1eafn v\u1edbi chu k\u1ef3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd nh\u01b0 danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2010, Euro 2008, 2012&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">BLV Quang Huy c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh TBN s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt h\u01a1n B\u0110N d\u00f9 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 EURO 2016 \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi Cristiano Ronaldo trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u00f4ng l\u1ea1i nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i. &ldquo;Tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n lu\u00f4n r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y 2 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd h\u00f2a 1-1&rdquo;, BLV Quang Huy d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 6 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2002 t\u1edbi nay, v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00e1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng l\u00e0 2 th\u1eafng, 2 h\u00f2a v\u00e0 2 b\u1ea1i. 4/6 cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 b\u00e0n. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n m\u00e0 BLV Quang Huy \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-1h-ngay-166-khi-bo-tot-lac-loi-421-188527.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/nhan-dinh-bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-1h-ngay-166-khi-bo-tot-lac-loi.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-1h-ngay-166-khi-bo-tot-lac-loi-421-188527.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha (1h ng\u00e0y 16/6): Khi &ldquo;B\u00f2 t\u00f3t&rdquo; l\u1ea1c l\u1ed1i&hellip;</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 2 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i HLV Lopetegui. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng h\u1ec7 l\u1ee5y gh\u00ea g\u1edbm v\u00e0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \" open=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"187","checkdouble":"188539"},{"date":"11:09 15/06","title":"Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n MU s\u1ebd c\u00e0i c\u1eafm khi b\u00e1n Martial","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/tiet-lo-dieu-khoan-mu-se-cai-cam-khi-ban-martial.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man United s\u1ebd c\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean mua l\u1ea1i Martial trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u1ecfi Old Trafford h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>MU t\u00ednh b\u00e1n Martial</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n MU s\u1ebd c\u00e0i c\u1eafm khi b\u00e1n Martial h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n MU s\u1ebd c\u00e0i c\u1eafm khi b\u00e1n Martial h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/13/tiet-lo-dieu-khoan-mu-se-cai-cam-khi-ban-martial.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU s\u1ebd b\u00e1n Martial h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Lamboley x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Martial \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay \u201cNh\u00e0 h\u00e1t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1\u201d h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u00d4ng cho r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Alexis Sanchez \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00f4ng l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn Martial m\u1ea5t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 sa s\u00fat.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t 18 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Premier League m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua. V\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 Martial \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tham d\u1ef1 World Cup c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Martial v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a HLV Mourinho \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Man United c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 Martial ra \u0111i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Mourinho s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Martial mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. V\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1eafng nghe nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i.</div>\r\n<h2>Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00e0i c\u1eafm th\u00eam c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Metro \u0111\u01b0a tin r\u1eb1ng Man United s\u1ebd c\u00e0i th\u00eam \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ea7n tr\u0103m ti\u1ec1n ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1ebfu c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c b\u00e1n Martial sau \u0111\u00f3. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Martial mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Man United lo ng\u1ea1i r\u1eb1ng Martial c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c. V\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf d\u0129 nhi\u00ean s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb 22 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ng\u1eb7t ngh\u00e8o.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Ed Woodward l\u00ean n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n n\u0103m 2013, Man United th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00ednh k\u00e8m nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n v\u00e0o trong c\u00e1c h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n h\u01b0\u1edfng 25% ti\u1ec1n ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau n\u00e0y v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u00e1n Michael Keane cho Burnley n\u0103m 2015. Man United c\u0169ng c\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua l\u1ea1i khi b\u00e1n Depay cho Lyon v\u00e0o n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU kh\u00e1c:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-se-de-martial-roi-mu-voi-mot-dieu-kien-172-188464.html\">Mourinho s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 Martial r\u1eddi MU v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-vu-sao-khung-psg-172-188458.html\">MU nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c m\u1eebng v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng PSG</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"186","checkdouble":"188540"},{"date":"10:52 15/06","title":"QBV Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2017: \u201cT\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/25/qbv-viet-nam-2017-tay-ban-nha-se-co-3-diem-truoc-bo-dao-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, QBV Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2017 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110inh Thanh Trung \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u00e0 c\u1ef1u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.</h2><h2>&ldquo;T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha&rdquo;</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng Telstar 18 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u0103n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng 5-0 c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i qua 14/6, m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay, NHM th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec9nh cao c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u00e0 t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00fa \u00fd s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn th\u01b0 h\u00f9ng r\u1ef1c l\u1eeda gi\u1eefa hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"QBV Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2017 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"QBV Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2017 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/25/len-ngoi-sieu-cup-qg-dinh-thanh-trung-muon-tao-ky-tich-tren-dt-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110inh Thanh Trung d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u1eadn&nbsp;</span>B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, QBV Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u0103m 2017 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110inh Thanh Trung \u0111\u00e3 cho r\u1eb1ng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch EURO 2016 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t TBN \u0111ang khao kh\u00e1t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua cu\u1ed9c kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Brazil l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 1 cho danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. \u1ee8ng vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 2 theo t\u00f4i l\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p n\u00ean s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i HLV ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd World Cup khai m\u00e0n c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o th\u00eam s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c World Cup 2018&rdquo;, Thanh Trung t\u00e2m s\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ramos-phat-bieu-soc-truoc-tran-tay-ban-nha-vs-bo-dao-nha-421-188529.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/ramos-phat-bieu-soc-truoc-tran-tay-ban-nha-vs-bo-dao-nha.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ramos-phat-bieu-soc-truoc-tran-tay-ban-nha-vs-bo-dao-nha-421-188529.html\">Ramos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng B, th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Sergio Ramos \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League n\u0103m nay khi x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 6/14, tuy nhi\u00ean theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110inh Thanh Trung, anh c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n Ph\u00fac t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n theo d\u00f5i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup, d\u00f9 v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng t\u1ea1i V-League.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;L\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u00fd th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp th\u1eddi gian c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 sinh ho\u1ea1t.<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vck-world-cup-2018/lich-thi-dau-41.html\" target=\"_blank\"> L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u World Cup 2018 </span>c\u0169ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i theo d\u00f5i nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe cho c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">World Cup c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng x\u1eed l\u00fd t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>HLV Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n Ph\u00fac tin v\u00e0o \u00fd th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm. Tr\u1eadn khuya mu\u1ed9n th\u00ec xem l\u1ea1i th\u00f4i v\u00ec c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef s\u1ee9c cho bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp s\u00e1ng h\u00f4m sau&quot;, Thanh Trung chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0110inh Thanh Trung v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c x\u1ecf gi\u00e0y ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 14 V-League. Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n HAGL \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc, tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 \u0111ang kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u0103ng hoa v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u 17/6.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/blv-quang-huy-du-doan-the-nao-ve-tran-bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-421-188539.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/blv-quang-huy-du-doan-the-nao-ve-tran-bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/blv-quang-huy-du-doan-the-nao-ve-tran-bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-421-188539.html\">BLV Quang Huy d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng B gi\u1eefa B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha, BLV Quang Huy \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa hai qu\u1ed1c gia tr\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \" open=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"185","checkdouble":"188541"}]}